data.description: This charming home located in the sought after Surprise Valley in SE Boise.  welcomes you with an inviting front porch, open floorplan, with hardwood floors throughout, open great room with vaulted ceilings and a a fire place. Kitchen features updated granite countertops ,stainless appliances, fridge, gas range and large island.  Spacious master suite with walk in closet and fully remodeled bathroom with dual vanities.  Upstairs you will find a secondary master upstairs, featuring walk in closet and bathrooms.  Secondary master has easy, private access, making it a great option in a shared living situation. Neighborhood features two community pools, community center, abundant green space and walking trails. Highly sought after school district and location! Just minutes from Lucky Peak, the Greenbelt, Boise River, Barber Park and multiple East Boise restaurants.
